O(1).
@End Performance_Hints
@Security_Scope
Owns payloads.
@End Security_Scope
Process called "sql_create_table" takes table as Integer, columns as Integer, constraints as Integer, options as Integer returns Integer:
    Return proc sql_alloc with SQL_STMT_CREATE_TABLE, table, columns, constraints, options
End Process

